# Nexus Recipe DSL
# PROFILE|scope|key|value
# MEMORY|scope|type|ttl|pin|tags|content
# CALL|task|prompt
# CODEGEN|task|output|overwrite|prompt
# TOOL|tool-name|k=v;k2=v2

PROFILE|global|response_tone|Concise, technical, and direct
PROFILE|project|code_style|Prefer small single-purpose methods
MEMORY|project|SKILL|365|true|architecture,services|Use service layer validation before DAO writes
CALL|GENERAL_CHAT|Summarize what was configured in this recipe in 3 bullets
CODEGEN|CODE_GENERATION|src/main/java/com/nexus/service/GeneratedHealthService.java|false|Create a GeneratedHealthService class with method public String status() returning "ok".
TOOL|fs.read|path=README.md;maxchars=300
